Package: shellgame
Title: The Shell Game - Audit Geographic Data Transformations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Phinn", "Markson",
    email = "markson.2@osu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9169-6095"))
Description: Reveals how data quality silently degrades during geographic
    transformations while variable labels remain unchanged. Demonstrates that
    transformation error is agnostic to both the variable (population, income,
    etc.) and the tool (R, Python, etc.). Provides a reproducible audit
    framework for quantifying the shift from observed to imputed data at each
    transformation hop.
